Hypo Chief Aims to Sell Italy Unit Within 24 Months, Profil Says

-- B y   Z o e   S c h n e e w e i s s
-- 
2011-04-22T08:22:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-22/hypo-chief-aims-to-sell-italy-unit-within-24-months-profil-says.html
Hypo Alpe-Adria-Bank International
AG Chief Executive OfficerGottwald Kranebitter aims to sell the
lender’s Italian unit within 24 months, Profil reported, citing
an interview.  The Hypo Alpe CEO said he was counting on the Austrian unit
“reprivatizing as soon as possible,” according to the report.  According to European Union requirements, Hypo Alpe, which
was taken over by the state in 2009, has to be sold again by the
end of 2014, Vienna-based Profil said.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
